#: data/campaigns/Delfadors_Memoirs/scenarios/14_Shadows.cfg:51
#: data/campaigns/Delfadors_Memoirs/scenarios/14_Shadows.cfg:78
#: data/campaigns/Delfadors_Memoirs/scenarios/14_Shadows.cfg:106
